These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: indonesian, australian, dutch, japanese
1. Nationality:australian is in an odd position##4
2. Nationality:japanese is between Nationality:indonesian and Nationality:australian##2
3. Nationality:japanese is on the right of Nationality:indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | indonesian | japanese | australian | dutch |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Food: eggplant, papaya, blueberry, cherry
1. Food:eggplant is on the left of Food:cherry##1
2. Food:papaya is in an odd position##4
3. Food:papaya is on the left or right of Food:eggplant##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | papaya | eggplant | cherry | blueberry |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
Movie-Genre: animation, action, fantasy, scientific
1. Movie-Genre:scientific is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:animation##3
2. Movie-Genre:animation is in an odd position##4
3. Movie-Genre:fantasy is between Movie-Genre:scientific and Movie-Genre:action##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | scientific | fantasy | action |

