.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Food: banana, watermelon, lemon, lettuce
1. Food:watermelon == Food:watermelon##1
2. Food:lettuce is on the left or right of Food:lemon##3
3. Food:lemon is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:banana is in an even position##4
5. Food:lettuce is on the left of Food:watermelon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | lemon | lettuce | watermelon | banana |

